                 person("Gael", "Yvert")),
         journal = "PloS Genetics",
         year = 2016,
         volume = "",
         pages = "accepted",
         key = "Chuffar2016",

         textVersion =
         paste("Chuffart et al. (2016) Exploiting single-cell",
               "quantitative data to map genetic variants having",
               "probabilistic effects. PLoS Genetics (in revision)")
         )


